    conv_lhs => rw [show rotproj_outer_unit P pc.w = (fun x => ⟪rotM (x 0) (x 1) P, pc.w⟫ / ‖P‖) by rfl]
    rw [fderiv_div_const (hdiff.differentiableAt)]
    simp only [ContinuousLinearMap.smul_apply, smul_eq_mul, Fin.isValue]
    field_simp
    ring_nf
    congr 1
    · rfl
    · rfl
```
